The paper discusses combinatorial descriptions of geometric structures and their applications in designing efficient geometric algorithms. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Computational Geometry (cs.CG) sub-category. Additionally, the paper mentions regular labelings, which are often used in graph theory and combinatorics, suggesting that the paper may also belong to the Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Discrete Mathematics (cs.DM), Graph Theory (cs.GT), and/or Computational Complexity (cs.CC) sub-categories.
